            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "لَيْسَ عِنْدَهُ مَا اُشْتُرِيَ مِنْهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:2:5:30",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/27/30",
      "text": [
        " \"لاَ بَأْسَ إِذَا أَوْفَاهُ اَلْوَزْنَ اَلَّذِي اُشْتُرِطَ عَلَيْهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4020 - Abu al-Sabbah al-Kinani asked Imam (as) about a man who bought one hundred mann of brass for a specified price, while the seller did not possess the quantity sold at the time of the transaction.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm as long as he delivers the specified weight that was agreed upon.\""
        ]
      }
    },
